Eliza Whitlock White, Respondent v. The New York Elevated Railroad Company, et al., Appellants. *492Decided December 17, 1891. Appeal by defendants from judgment entered upon decision of at equity term. Davies & Rapallo, attorneys, and J. C. Thomson of counsel, for appellants. G. Willett Van Nest, for respondent.

Before McAdam and Gildersleeve, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Judgment affirmed, with costs.
